It's not really fair that group of highly mobile casters can move and kill a dragon within just a few minutes and then make a killing by holding the epic pieces for another class hostage.  The basic fact of the matter is, MB wizards can do this with ease and near impunity.  Yeah, Rangers can do some amazing damage too, but they can't port themselves and there are a bunch of restrictions on ranged weapons.<br>
<br>
There are a bunch of epics that need fundamental changes in how they are set up.  Quillmane for Mages, Severilious for Warriors, to a lesser extent Gorenaire for Pallys and Bards (although Vox is a good alternate source for them), there's one or two for the Enchanter epic as well.  Long waits for spawns that may or may not drop your piece and that are likely to be ks'd.<br>
<br>
Manaburn doesn't need to be nerfed (you all on PvP servers can argue about it in PvP combat if you want), VI needs to take a look at what manaburn has done to Kunark era content and make some changes.  32k hit point dragons are simply too easy to kill by a few people who can do that much damage in under 10 seconds. <p>Hyardgune Varangian <BR> 57 Ogre Myrmidon of Gathered Might</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=1790.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=1790.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=1790.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=1790.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=1790.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=1790.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a> <b>7</b> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=1790.topic&start=141&stop=160>8</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=1790.topic&start=161&stop=180>9</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=1790.topic&start=181&stop=200>10</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=1790.topic&start=201&stop=210>11</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showPrevMessage?topicID=1790.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showNextMessage?topicID=1790.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br>